sudden
thunderI
stood
motionless
, but my agitation was too
violent to be of any long duration.
A natural tear I
shed
, but wip'd it
soon
.
IT was your
goodness
, and the
humanity
of your family, that
sheltered
the wretched
Maria
, and provided for the
helpless
Harriot
Your feelings are your reward.
FROM all the variegated
